      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "code": {
          "language": "markdown",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "# k6 stress overview\nThis dashboard expects k6 metrics sent to Prometheus remote write.\n\nRecommended run shape:\n\n```bash\nK6_PROMETHEUS_RW_SERVER_URL=http://localhost:9090/api/v1/write \\\nK6_PROMETHEUS_RW_TREND_STATS=p(95),p(99),avg,max \\\nK6_PROMETHEUS_RW_STALE_MARKERS=true \\\nk6 run -o experimental-prometheus-rw --tag testid=<unique-run-id> script.js\n```\n\nUse `testid` to isolate one run from another. `scenario` becomes useful when the k6 script defines multiple scenarios.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.4.2",
      "title": "Run Notes",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "none"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 4,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "percentChangeColorMode": "standard",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "showPercentChange": false,
        "textMode": "auto",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.4.2",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource}"
          },
          "expr": "sum(k6_vus{testid=~\"$testid\",scenario=~\"$scenario\"})",
          "legendFormat": "vus",
